edBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T09:52:07.000Z","msg":"佢都算係youtube第一愛國五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83d71f41c9ae323ae9ba5de42cb667f255868d6c","tid":2451691,"uid":75823,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"b6be8c7c1e1662187b3a2c8d61b3c02de0c82333","tid":2451691,"uid":391580,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"70ae7629c02ca1a4d0e2aae8f866c0b13facfb6b","tid":2451691,"uid":195169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T09:47:35.000Z","msg":"鐵拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T09:49:29.000Z","msg":"條友其實腦筋清醒<br />\n講嘢有邏輯<br />\n估計其實都係為咗錢所以奶共<br />\n<br />\n酒後吐真言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢最後好似仲話如果兩個月解決唔到佢屋企土地嘅事佢就自焚"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T09:58:18.000Z","msg":"根本支國邊有真心五毛, 個個都知共匪咩料啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左教育程度好底既人"},{"pid":"ed6e380920e9bc277cf052a203a9d9a32572b258","tid":2451691,"uid":391580,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T09:58:31.000Z","msg":"上面打漏咗一個好精彩嘅問答<br />\n<br />\n小粉紅：（討論到官員刪帖）他是個官員他還要有工作能力呢....之後就被打斷咗<br />\n<br />\n鄭國成：什麼能力？什麼工作能力？什麼能力？<br />\n連老百姓問題都解決不了的什麼工作能力<br />\n什麼能力？<br />\n什麼能力？<br />\n你別給我發病，什麼能力？<br />\n什麼能力？<br />\n什麼能力？<br />\n<br />\n小粉紅：說白了...（又被打斷）<br />\n<br />\n鄭國成：什麼能力？別扯沒用的！什麼能力？<br />\n嗯？什麼能力？<br />\n啥也沒有！扯這些幹什麼？<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">滾！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e43b0da7e54592352e3a081bc1f1720089d100f3","tid":2451691,"uid":391580,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"83d71f41c9ae323ae9ba5de42cb667f255868d6c","tid":2451691,"uid":75823,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"b6be8c7c1e1662187b3a2c8d61b3c02de0c82333","tid":2451691,"uid":391580,"li